Maintainer: Steven R. Talbot <talbot.steven@mh-hannover.de>
Description: The packages uses tabular data from rat epilepsy studies and applies a composite measures schemes (via PCA) to select the most prominent 
   features. Further, variables can be selected to perform cluster analysis on a selected subset of variables (composite score) to assess the cluster
   distribution of severity in various experimental states and animal models.
